PN,42902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1780989358
OL,3,CTeenager suffers life-threatening
OL,4,Cinjuries after three-vehicle crash
OL,6,FAn occupant of the BMW car ` a man
OL,7,Faged in his teens ` was found to have
OL,8,Fsustained life-threatening injuries.
OL,10,FHe was taken to hospital for treatment
OL,11,Fwhere he remains in a critical
OL,12,Fcondition.
OL,14,FTwo men and a woman also sustained
OL,15,Finjuries in the collision, and have
OL,16,Falso been taken to hospital for
OL,17,Ftreatment.
OL,19,FThe A1 has fully reopened this morning
OL,20,Fafter investigation works were carried
OL,21,Fout overnight.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/4
