PN,42903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1780989358
OL,3,CTeenager suffers life-threatening
OL,4,Cinjuries after three-vehicle crash
OL,6,FNorthumbria Police's Roads Policing
OL,7,FUnit are investigating the
OL,8,Fcircumstances around the collision and
OL,9,Fare appealing for anyone to get in
OL,10,Ftouch they haven't yet spoken with.
OL,12,FOfficers want to hear from anyone who
OL,13,Fmay have witnessed the collision or
OL,14,Fthe three vehicles in the moments
OL,15,Fprior, and anyone who has dash cam or
OL,16,FCCTV footage from the area.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/4
